                <note rend="inline" type="source">693.119/271: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in China</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Reinsch</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-05-21T18:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">May 21, 1919, 6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your May 17, 7 p.m.</p>
                <p>Matter will be taken up with Italian Government.</p>
                <p>In the meantime you may confer with your colleagues with a view to persuading the
                    Italian representative to recommend to his Government that the exception be
                    withdrawn. Uniformity of action is most essential.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Polk</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
